  <!-- EN: ground-penetrating scanner -->
  <GroundPenetratingScanner.label>地質掃描器</GroundPenetratingScanner.label>
  <!-- EN: Build ground-penetrating scanners that can detect drillable resources under the surface. Requires an advanced component to construct. -->
  <GroundPenetratingScanner.description>建造地質掃描器，可以掃描出地底下的礦物資源。建造需要高級零件。</GroundPenetratingScanner.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->geophysics</li>
    <li>subject->ground-penetrating scanners</li>
    <li>subject_story->discovered the bones of ancient giants, far below the planet's surface</li>
    <li>subject_story->stumbled across a rich gold seam whilst scanning for tin and became fabulously wealthy</li>
    <li>subject_story->scanned the ground for ancient minefields, to protect the people</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->constructing geophysical scanners</li>
  -->
  <GroundPenetratingScanner.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->地球物理學</li>
    <li>subject->地質掃描器</li>
    <li>subject_story->發現位於地球深處的遠古巨人骨頭</li>
    <li>subject_story->在掃描錫礦時偶然發現了豐富的金礦，並變得非常富有</li>
    <li>subject_story->為保諼人民而掃描地面，偵測遠古的雷區</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->建造地質掃描器</li>
  </GroundPenetratingScanner.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
