  <!-- EN: long-range mineral scanner -->
  <LongRangeMineralScanner.label>長程礦物掃描器</LongRangeMineralScanner.label>
  <!-- EN: Construct long-range mineral scanners your researchers can use to detect precious minerals across the planet. Can be tuned to find a specific mineral. Requires advanced components to construct. -->
  <LongRangeMineralScanner.description>長程礦物掃描器能夠探測出區域以外的珍貴礦物。可調整找到特定礦物。建造需要高級零件。</LongRangeMineralScanner.description>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>subject->long-range mineral detection</li>
    <li>subject_story->built so many scanners that the planet's entire geology was revealed</li>
    <li>subject_story->discovered with a scanner what the other settlements were mining and made huge profits through trading</li>
    <li>subject_story->mined out the entirety of the planet's jade for religious effigies</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->constructing long-range mineral scanners</li>
  -->
  <LongRangeMineralScanner.generalRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>subject->長程礦物掃描</li>
    <li>subject_story->建造了很多台掃描儀來揭示整個星球的地質情況</li>
    <li>subject_story->用掃描器發現其他據點正在開採的礦物，並透過交易賺取巨額利潤</li>
    <li>subject_story->開採了星球上所有的翡翠來製作宗教偶像</li>
    <li>subject_gerund->建造長程礦物掃描器</li>
  </LongRangeMineralScanner.generalRules.rulesStrings>
  
